def nyi1(df): 
    nyi1_counties = ['Chemung County', 'Broome County', 'Steuben County']
    return ((df['County'] == 'Tioga County') & (df['State'] == 'NY')) | df['County'].isin(nyi1_counties)
def nyi2(df):
    nyi2_counties = ['Cortland County', 'Chenango County', 'Schuyler County', 'Tompkins County', 'Yates County']
    return df['County'].isin(nyi2_counties)
def pa(df): 
    return ((df['County'] == 'Tioga County') & (df['State'] == 'PA')) | \
        (df['County'] == 'Bradford County') | \
        (df['County'] == 'Susquehanna County')
In [4]:
def all_counties(df):
    return nyi1(df) | nyi2(df) | pa(df)

# create a mapping from month abbreviations to quarter numbers
month_to_quarter = {'Jan': 1, 'Feb': 1, 'Mar': 1, 'Apr': 2, 'May': 2, 'Jun': 2, 
                    'Jul': 3, 'Aug': 3, 'Sep': 3, 'Oct': 4, 'Nov': 4, 'Dec': 4}

# create a new column 'Quarter' by mapping the 'Month' column to quarter numbers
df_emp['qtr_i'] = df_emp['Month'].map(month_to_quarter)
df_wge['qtr_i'] = df_wge['Quarter'].str.extract(r'Qtr(\d)').astype(int)

# merge wage and employment data
df_merged = pd.merge(df_emp, df_wge, on=['County', 'State', 'qtr_i', "Year"], how='inner')

def get_stats(df, select_func, name): 
    df_select = df[select_func(df)]
    desc_before_2008 = df_select[df_select['Year'] < 2008][['Employees', 'Wages']].describe()
    desc_after_2008 = df_select[df_select['Year'] >= 2008][['Employees', 'Wages']].describe()
    desc_before_2008.columns = pd.MultiIndex.from_product([['Before 2008'], desc_before_2008.columns])
    desc_after_2008.columns = pd.MultiIndex.from_product([['After 2008'], desc_after_2008.columns])
    df_summary = pd.concat([desc_before_2008, desc_after_2008], axis=1)
    df_summary.index.name = name
    return df_summary

url = "https://www2.census.gov/geo/docs/reference/codes/files/national_county.txt"

dtype_dict = {
    'State': str,
    'State_fips': str,
    'County_fips': str,
    'County': str, 
    'Other': str
}

%%stata
gen pa = State == "PA"
gen post2008 = Year >= 2008
gen pa_post2008 = pa * post2008

gen monthnum = month(date(Month, "M"))

sort monthnum

gen t = (Year - 2001) * 12 + monthnum
gen t2 = t^2

gen pai = (County == "Tioga County" && State == "PA") | County == "Bradford County" | County == "Susquehanna County"

gen nyi1 = (County == "Tioga County" && State == "NY")  | County == "Chemung County" | County == "Broome County" | County == "Steuben County"

gen nyi2 = County == "Cortland County" | County == "Chenango County" | County == "Schuyler County" | County == "Tompkins County" | County == "Yates County"

reg Employees pa post2008 pa_post2008 t t2 if Month != "Ann" 


//part 1 
// fist: all border
reg Employees pa post2008 pa_post2008 t t2 if Month != "Ann" & !nyi2
estimates save border_employee, replace
estimates store border_employee

//second: high intensity with border high intensity
reg Employees pa post2008 pa_post2008 t t2 if Month != "Ann" & (pai|nyi1)
estimates save hi_border_employee, replace
estimates store hi_border_employee

//third: high intesity PA with nonborder for spillover
reg Employees pa post2008 pa_post2008 t t2 if Month != "Ann" & (pai|nyi2)
estimates save hi_nonborder_employee, replace
estimates store hi_nonborder_employee


esttab border_employee hi_border_employee hi_nonborder_employee using "fracking.rtf", replace star(* 0.1 ** 0.05 *** 0.01)

%%stata
local year_list
local year_pa_list
forval i = 2008/2013 { 
	gen year`i' = Year == `i'
	gen year`i'_pa = year`i'*pa
	local year_pa_list `year_pa_list' year`i'_pa
	local year_list `year_list' year`i'
}

// Part 2
reg Employees pa `year_list' `year_pa_list' if Month != "Ann" & !nyi2
estimates save yearly_border_employee, replace
estimates store yearly_border_employee
reg Employees pa `year_list' `year_pa_list' if Month != "Ann" & (pai|nyi1)
estimates save yearly_hi_border_employee, replace
estimates store yearly_hi_border_employee
reg Employees pa `year_list' `year_pa_list' if Month != "Ann" & (pai|nyi2)
estimates save yearly_Hnonborder_emp, replace
estimates store yearly_Hnonborder_emp

# Extract the quarter number from the 'Quarter' column
df_wge = df_wge[~(df_wge['Quarter'] == 'Annu')]
df_wge['qtr_i'] = df_wge['Quarter'].str.extract(r'Qtr(\d)').astype(int)

# Calculate the total quarters from the 'Year' column
df_wge['qtr_tot'] = (df_wge['Year'] - df_wge['Year'].min()) * 4 + df_wge['qtr_i']
df_wge['t'] = df_wge['qtr_tot']
df_wge['t2'] = df_wge['t']**2

# generate dummy vars
df_wge['pai'] = \
    ((df_wge['County'] == 'Tioga County') & (df_wge['State'] == 'PA')) | \
    (df_wge['County'] == 'Bradford County') | \
    (df_wge['County'] == 'Susquehanna County')

# generate the rest of dummy vars 

# Define the counties for nyi1 and nyi2
nyi1_counties = ['Chemung County', 'Broome County', 'Steuben County']
nyi2_counties = ['Cortland County', 'Chenango County', 'Schuyler County', 'Tompkins County', 'Yates County']

# Create nyi1 and nyi2 columns
df_wge['nyi1'] = ((df_wge['County'] == 'Tioga County') & (df_wge['State'] == 'NY')) | df_wge['County'].isin(nyi1_counties)
df_wge['nyi2'] = df_wge['County'].isin(nyi2_counties)

# Create pa, post2008, and pa_post2008 columns
df_wge['pa'] = df_wge['State'] == 'PA'
df_wge['post2008'] = df_wge['Year'] >= 2008
df_wge['pa_post2008'] = df_wge['pa'] & df_wge['post2008']
